data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Tucked away on a private street in the heart of beautiful Shady Cove, you will find this well maintained home. The way the home is placed on the land allows for ample RV parking and a garage for the toys. There is a large deck and back yard for entertaining and a fenced garden area. As you enter into the well laid out home you will see that is it nicely updated with newer range and flooring in guest bath. Other upgrades to this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home includes, new well pump and wiring in 2023, recently serviced water heater, and new gutters on the house. Seller is in the process of repainting the deck weather permitting. This is a must see.
